258f4abf1a92a2","tid":732542,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:02:37.000Z","msg":"iced coffee 係咪唔新鮮既shot 倒埋一齊而成?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:04:14.000Z","msg":"而家轉咗做美式咖啡(shot+水+冰)同cold brew"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"I mean d shot 係咪唔新鮮?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a31740ff6700d81bb9e98c0b30041f42895fbc","tid":732542,"uid":33567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:16:49.000Z","msg":"成日見啲師奶唔識講英文 用廣東話叫 啲staff會話依啲無㗎喎<br />\n做Starbucks居然睇唔起個師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05d15161dec1258ec2097567a8223e27f48e0a6","tid":732542,"uid":4438,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:40:35.000Z","msg":"星期六去文化中心等老婆睇完表演.<br />\n去買杯野想上網咁啦.<br />\n咁我係會員. 本身個APP 就Off 左print receipt <br />\n但我想上網. 叫佢print 張receipt 俾我.<br />\n個收銀員多多聲氣.<br />\n又話下次係APP 度開返Print Receipt <br />\n我話 '我唔係成日想要Receipt, 我想要wifi code'<br />\n佢話咁其實可以係app 度睇返.<br />\n我話&quot;個app 要買完野成10分鐘先update 個transaction record, 我想依家就上網&quot;<br />\n佢話&quot;唔緊要啦你下次開返個print receipt 啦, 今次print 俾你&quot;<br />\n<br />\n嘩...<br />\n真係好想開鳩佢波...<br />\n做乜jack 叫佢print 張receipt 好似要佢擔泥咁.<br />\n<br />\n其實好多做Starbucks 的都做到死老豆咁樣.<br />\n特別D 旺區.<br />\n記得柯士旬道果間又係好撚閪.<br />\n行埋去, 唔係講乜野歡迎光臨.<br />\n&quot;點呀?&quot;<br />\n咁同我講野...<br />\n<br />\n我話要杯Venti latte 熱o既<br />\n唔出聲, 拎我張starbucks card<br />\ndo 完<br />\n多謝唔講乜都唔講.<br />\n之後就講 &quot;下一位&quot;<br />\n<br />\n真係閪中之閪...<br />\n<br />\n冇乜野我都係Mobile Order 算."},{"pid":"d1f59d905009ebe6c3fa2de5754d53cfc225278f","tid":732542,"uid":40428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"Latte +cream 係咪好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127759ad7da889f2528adb7b7d81717bd7da8418","tid":732542,"uid":73787,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d1f59d905009ebe6c